&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Portfolio of hands-on projects—Formula SAE, SolarCar, Robotics, CubeSats, or other club/personal builds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Proficient with modern CAD software and version control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Strong analytical mindset, first-principles problem solving, and clear communication&lt;/li&gt;
