&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Your projects demonstrate not just mechanical engineering aptitude but also multidisciplinary knowledge of electrical engineering and software engineering concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
