&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SHIPPING &amp;amp; RECEIVING SPECIALIST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mesh Optical Technologies was founded on the belief that optical photons will be at the center of advanced technologies in the coming century. Making advanced technology ubiquitous means building at scale, and that’s exactly what we’re doing at Mesh.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Receiving Specialist to support the full lifecycle of incoming materials.. This is a hands-on role— you&#39;ll work closely with engineering, operations, and purchasing to make sure the right materials are in the right place at the right time. This is a ground-floor opportunity: you won&#39;t just maintain a system, you&#39;ll help us build one and improve it over time.&lt;/p&gt;
