&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and repair defective assemblies to improve yield&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain proper handling of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;ESD-sensitive and optical components&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;cleanroom protocols&lt;/strong&gt;, including gowning and contamination control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record build data and defects for process tracking and continuous improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineering and production teams to optimize processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
