&lt;li&gt;Lead supplier-side root-cause analysis and corrective action for quality, yield, and reliability issues, driving improvements that directly impact product performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-develop new manufacturing processes with suppliers for challenging components and assemblies, translating internal design intent into producible supplier workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with mechanical, optical, process, and manufacturing engineering teams to ensure supplier capabilities align with product requirements and production ramp timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report supplier performance metrics (quality, delivery, yield, responsiveness) and drive accountability against targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support supplier capacity planning and production ramp execution for new product introductions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
