&lt;li&gt;Strong fundamentals in mechanical engineering, manufacturing processes, or semiconductor/photonic fabrication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with external suppliers or contract manufacturers in a technical capacity, or demonstrated strong aptitude and motivation to develop supplier management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read and interpret engineering drawings, including GD&amp;amp;T&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and problem-solving skills, with comfort working across organizational boundaries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to work extended hours and weekends as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel to supplier sites as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
